<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Web | Portfolio</title><link>https://k1lgor.github.io/tag/web/</link><atom:link href="https://k1lgor.github.io/tag/web/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><description>Web</description><generator>Wowchemy (https://wowchemy.com)</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 23 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><image><url>https://k1lgor.github.io/media/icon_hucdc783dfe6b607fdadcda92cca688f51_1481_512x512_fill_lanczos_center_3.png</url><title>Web</title><link>https://k1lgor.github.io/tag/web/</link></image><item><title>Manchester United Stats</title><link>https://k1lgor.github.io/project/manutd-stats/</link><pubDate>Mon, 23 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://k1lgor.github.io/project/manutd-stats/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dragos IT Academy</title><link>https://k1lgor.github.io/project/flask-project/</link><pubDate>Thu, 12 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://k1lgor.github.io/project/flask-project/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="setup">Setup&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>To set up the Flask application, follow these steps:&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>Clone the repository to your local machine:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git clone https://github.com/k1lgor/flask.git
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="2">
&lt;li>Change into the flask directory:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> flask
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="3">
&lt;li>Create a virtual environment and install the required dependencies:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">python -m venv venv
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">source&lt;/span> venv/bin/activate
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pip install -r requirements.txt
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>This will create a virtual environment and install all the necessary dependencies specified in the requirements.txt file.&lt;/p>
&lt;ol start="4">
&lt;li>Start the Flask application:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">flask run
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>The application will be accessible at &lt;a href="http://localhost:5000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:5000&lt;/a> in your web browser.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Portfolio</title><link>https://k1lgor.github.io/project/portfolio/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://k1lgor.github.io/project/portfolio/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Login Page</title><link>https://k1lgor.github.io/project/login-page/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://k1lgor.github.io/project/login-page/</guid><description/></item><item><title>ToDo app</title><link>https://k1lgor.github.io/project/todo-vuejs/</link><pubDate>Fri, 11 Mar 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://k1lgor.github.io/project/todo-vuejs/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>